<v-container fluid grid-list-md>

    <v-flex d-flex xs12 sm12 md12 xl12 lg12>

          <v-btn
            slot="activator"
            color="primary"
            dark

            Sortieren nach:

            </v-list-tile>
          </v-list>

          hide-details
          append-icon="search"
          single-line
          color="red"
          >
        </v-text-field>
      </v-toolbar>
      </v-flex>
            </v-layout>

  
  <v-layout row wrap>

              <v-list-tile-sub-title v-html="patient.priority"></v-list-tile-sub-title>

        </template>
      </v-list>
  </v-flex>
